pakaian yang bersih...

457
00:47:58,470 --> 00:48:00,330
Dia menggigitku!

458
00:48:08,840 --> 00:48:12,340
Apa kalian belum
selesai mendandaninya?

459
00:48:12,340 --> 00:48:15,650
Dia bukan manusia.

460
00:48:15,650 --> 00:48:18,180
Dia binatang.

461
